  "text": "All mouse experiments were carried out in compliance with German law and according to the guidelines approved by the Bezirksregierung Braunschweig or Landesamt für Gesundheit und Soziales Berlin. Both male and female mouse embryos were used. Sip1 conditional mutants carried a loxP flanked exon 7 crossed to either Nex or Emx1-Cre [CITATION_1] Higashi et al., 2002; [CITATION_2] . The Ntf3 mutant was kindly provided by Dr Michael Sendtner (University of Würzburg, Germany).",
